---
import Layout from '../../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---
<Layout title="ScanLabel - Ingredient Scanner" description="AI-powered food label reader. Scan ingredients, get A-F safety grade, personal allergy alerts. Free.">
  <div class="pt-24 min-h-screen">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 py-16">
      <a href="/en/apps" class="text-sm text-text-muted hover:text-accent-purple transition-colors">&larr; All apps</a>

      <div class="flex items-center gap-6 mt-8 mb-12">
        <img src="/apps/labelwise-icon.png" alt="ScanLabel icon" width="128" height="128" class="rounded-[28px] shadow-lg" />
        <div>
          <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-3"><span class="gradient-text">ScanLabel</span></h1>
          <p class="text-xl text-text-muted">AI-Powered Food Label Reader</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="card-hover p-8 rounded-xl border border-border bg-bg-card mb-8">
        <p class="text-text-muted leading-relaxed mb-6">
          Point your camera at any food label and know exactly what you're eating. ScanLabel scans ingredients with OCR, explains every additive in plain language, and gives the product an A-F safety grade — personalized to your dietary needs.
        </p>
        <p class="text-text-muted leading-relaxed mb-6">
          Most people can't pronounce half the ingredients on the label, let alone know if they're safe. ScanLabel recognizes 236 E-numbers and additives, flags your personal allergens, and tells you whether that snack deserves a spot in your cart — or back on the shelf.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-lg font-bold text-white mb-4">Scan. Understand. Decide.</h2>
        <p class="text-text-muted leading-relaxed mb-6">
          Standing in the grocery aisle wondering if something is safe for you? Point, scan, done. ScanLabel highlights what matters to YOU — gluten, lactose, nuts, whatever your concern. No more squinting at tiny print or googling E-numbers on the spot.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-lg font-bold text-white mb-4">Features</h2>
        <ul class="space-y-3 text-text-muted mb-6">
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <span class="text-accent-green mt-1">&#10003;</span>
            <span><strong class="text-white">OCR Label Scanning</strong> — point your camera at any ingredient list. Instant recognition, even on crumpled packaging</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <span class="text-accent-green mt-1">&#10003;</span>
            <span><strong class="text-white">236 E-Numbers Decoded</strong> — every additive explained in plain language. Know what you're really eating</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <span class="text-accent-green mt-1">&#10003;</span>
            <span><strong class="text-white">A-F Safety Grade</strong> — instant overall score for the product. A = clean, F = think twice</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <span class="text-accent-green mt-1">&#10003;</span>
            <span><strong class="text-white">Dietary Profile</strong> — set up your allergies and dietary restrictions once. Every scan is personalized from that point</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <span class="text-accent-green mt-1">&#10003;</span>
            <span><strong class="text-white">Personal Alerts</strong> — instant warnings when a product contains YOUR allergens. Never miss a hidden ingredient</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <span class="text-accent-green mt-1">&#10003;</span>
            <span><strong class="text-white">Scan History</strong> — all your scanned products saved. Compare, revisit, track what you buy</span>
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="card-hover p-8 rounded-xl border border-border bg-bg-card mb-8">
        <h2 class="text-lg font-bold text-white mb-4">Coming to App Store</h2>
        <p class="text-text-muted">ScanLabel is preparing for release. Free for iOS.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="card-hover p-8 rounded-xl border border-border bg-bg-card mb-8">
        <h2 class="text-lg font-bold text-white mb-4">Privacy</h2>
        <p class="text-text-muted mb-3">All scanning and analysis happens on your device. No images or ingredient data are sent to any server. Your dietary profile stays on your phone.</p>
        <a href="/apps/labelwise/privacy" class="text-sm text-accent-purple hover:underline">Privacy Policy &rarr;</a>
      </div>

      <div class="text-sm text-text-muted">
        <p>Questions or feedback: <a href="mailto:magic4e@gmail.com" class="text-accent-purple hover:underline">magic4e@gmail.com</a></p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>
